        `,
      },
      {
        question: "How do I book a session and what is the payment structure?",
        answer: `
          <p>Our booking process is designed to be simple and transparent:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>1. Enquiry:</strong> Fill out the
              <a href="/contact/">contact form</a> with a few details about your project
