            </li>
          </ul>
        `,
      },
      {
        question: "What happens if I need to reschedule or cancel?",
        answer: `
          <p>
            We understand that life happens and staff get sick, so we aim to be as flexible as possible.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Rescheduling:</strong> If you notify us at least <strong>48 hours in advance</strong>,
            we can transfer your deposit to a new date within the next 3 months (subject to availability).
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Weather:</strong> For outdoor portrait sessions, if Perth’s weather turns bad
