  {
    id: "deliverables-technical",
    title: "Deliverables & Technical Info",
    icon: Icons.deliverables,
    intro:
      "What you receive after the shoot, how long we keep files and how copyright works.",
    items: [
      {
        question: 'What is the "All Good Original Photos" inclusion?',
        answer: `
          <p>
            Most photographers only supply a small set of final edited images (for example, 10–20 photos).
